<p class="basetext"><strong>Item #:</strong> SCP-042-IT</p>

<p class="basetext"><strong>Object Class:</strong> <span class="text">Safe</span></p>

<p class="basetext"><strong>Special Containment Procedures:</strong> SCP-042-IT is contained in a laptop with anomalous origins, designated SCP-042-IT-1, which has been acquired and later secured by the Foundation. SCP-042-IT-1 is placed inside the C-042 anechoic chamber at <a href="http://scp-int.wikidot.com/siti-italiani#Sito-Minerva" target="_blank">Site Minerva</a>. Access to SCP-042-IT-1 is allowed only with Level 4 or higher clearance.</p>

<p class="basetext">Given the item's properties, information on the nature of SCP-042-IT must be filtered in the manner established by the D3EP-M1ND Protocol. Subjects exposed to SCP-042-IT-ψ without prior inoculation of the Klein-Mandelbrot memetic visual agent must be sedated and receive an Ω Class amnestic therapy (irreversible total amnesia). If they're confirmed to have been converted in SCP-042-IT-3 instances, they must be terminated.</p>
